content.rendered:
Come join us for a cold one and get out of the heat!

Thursday, September 21st, 4:00-:5:30pm.

Delaney’s Irish Pub and Grill

6150 W. Eldorado Pkwy., McKinney, TX.

Please RSVP to Melanie Chaiken at mchaiken@allegiancetitle.com.
